===Adjective===
'''undifferentiated'''

# {{biology}} describes [[tissue]]s where the individual [[cell]]s have not yet developed mature or distinguishing features, or describes [[embryonic]] [[organism]]s where the [[organ]]s cannot be identified.
# {{botany}} describes a [[plant]] [[body]] where the [[vascular tissue]] has not developed, as in the [[thallophyte]]s

